* Colton Software Fireworkz - Help *

You are seeing this text help file as no browser was
available to display the HTML help file. It may be
helpful to run a browser and then display Help again.


* Online Resources *

Many resources for Fireworkz are available online:

The Fireworkz Getting Started Guide
may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/docs/fireworkz/getting_started/

The Fireworkz User Guide
may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/docs/fireworkz/user_guide/

Updated Fireworkz packages and example files,
including those used in the Getting Started Guide,
may be obtained from
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/fireworkz/downloads/

Hints and Tips on using Fireworkz
may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/fireworkz/hints_and_tips/

Addenda and Errata to the printed documentation
may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/fireworkz/addenda_and_errata/


* Support *

Fireworkz is now open source and completely free to use,
so support is a self-help affair.
There is a Google Group colton-software-fireworkz
 Web site: http://groups.google.com/group/colton-software-fireworkz
 E-mail: colton-software-fireworkz@googlegroups.com
where you may seek help from other users.
Please include files which demonstrate any problems
(using a Spark or ZIP archive).


